## n8n@0.94.1 For a comprehensive list of changes, check out the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@0.94.0...n8n@0.94.1) for this version.
**Release date:** 2020-11-20 - Bug Fixes - GraphQL: Fixed an issue with the variables - WooCommerce Trigger: Fixed an issue with the webhook. The node now reuses a webhook if it already exists.
